name: Futuristic Cybernetic Buttons (Gaming) - FREEBIE
description:
As a big fan of cybernetic future and games, it motivated me to make a resource which can be used specifically for this genre of games.


An experiment using various techniques/workarounds to create fluid buttons and containers with shapes.


I would love to continue the project, but well - it's a start.


✉️ Feel free to contact me for dope projects.
